</div>
</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Murrow_and_William_Shirer.jpg" class="image" title="Edward R. Murrow and William L. Shirer, early 1950s."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/b0/Murrow_and_William_Shirer.jpg/180px-Murrow_and_William_Shirer.jpg" width="180" height="134" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Murrow_and_William_Shirer.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
